name: Zoom warns you when another meeting was created within the past 30 seconds

inline.description:
1. Open 2 mattermost session with users
2. As test user 1 start a Zoom meeting
3. As test user 2 start a Zoom meeting in the same channel
inline.expectedResult: For user 2 - The post created by Zoom warns you that a Zoom meeting was recently started and gives you the option to Create and Join

customFields.Important notes about this step: Note that this test can be run with Zomm configured using any authentication method.
